<p>「でも<span class="vocab">兄<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>兄</rb><rt>あに</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(older) brother</span></span>は<span class="vocab">近々<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>近々</rb><rt>きんきん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;soon; before long</span></span><span class="vocab">結婚いたします<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>結婚</rb><rt>けっこん</rt></ruby>いたします&nbsp;will marry</span></span>よ」</p>

