<p>その<span class="vocab">時<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>時</rb><rt>とき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;time; moment</span></span><span class="vocab">原口<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>原口</rb><rt>はらぐち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Haraguchi (name)</span></span>さんが、とうとう<span class="vocab">筆<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>筆</rb><rt>ふで</rt></ruby>&nbsp;brush</span></span>をおいて、</p>

